{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In charge of a junkyard, you have the opportunity to create a scrap empire. Buy cars, dismantle them to extract valuable parts, and sell them on the market. Every decision is crucial to find the perfect balance, maximizing your profits.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281630/extras/FerroVelhoSimulator_11_10_2024_16_38_43.png?t=1729256872\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Management</strong>: Manage your operations, make smart decisions about what to sell or store, and optimize the workflow of your junkyard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Trading and Profit</strong>: Sell parts or scrap, and keep an eye on market opportunities to maximize your earnings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cars</strong>: Work with a variety of cars, from common models to rare finds, each with unique parts and varying values.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Equipment</strong>: Upgrade your equipment to make it more efficient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration</strong>: Discover abandoned cars and hidden parts.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729256872","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281630/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729256872","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281630/86e36b00adb2c959379ae0b8d644eadb749158ac/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729256872","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281630/86e36b00adb2c959379ae0b8d644eadb749158ac/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729256872","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In charge of a junkyard, y